                             'Re_fle_chi' 1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  @{" Re_fle_chi " link play} is a Workbench game that is played on an 8 by 8
spaces game board that is divided in 4 'quadrants' of 4 by 4 spaces.
The goal is to move diagonal bars so they create a kaleidoscopic
pattern. As you click on a bar, 3 bars in the other quadrants will
also move. Complete the game in the least amount of moves.

  Have fun!

