@node play "The game: Installation/Playing"

                             Installation

  The installation is very simple, just place "Re_fle_chi" where you
want on your hard drive, floppy disk, Ram Disk, etc. No other files
or Libraries are needed.

                             How to play?

  The game board is divided in 4 'quadrants' of 4 by 4 spaces, and
diagonal bars fill the entire game board. The goal of the game is
to place bars so they make a kaleidoscopic pattern ...or the bars
have a mirror like pattern, from quadrant to quadrant.

  Clicking on any diagonal bar will change its state as well as the
state of one bar in each of the other quadrants, but those other
bars may not necessarily change the same bars, which complicates
the game a little. However, one thing is for certain: whatever bars
that are changed by one bar will always be the same when that bar
is changed again, until the game is completed.

  Complete the game in the least amount of moves possible.

  You can restart the game any time by clicikg on the 'New Game'
button or with the Right-Amiga and "N" keys combination.

  Have fun!

@endnode

